---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const updated = 'July 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Ozark Fulfillment"
  description="How Ozark Fulfillment collects, uses, and protects information submitted through our website."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="legal">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: {updated}</p>

      <p>
        Ozark Fulfillment ("we," "us," or "our") operates the website ozarkfulfillment.com.
        This policy explains what information we collect through the site and how we use it.
      </p>

      <h2>Information we collect</h2>
      <p>
        We only collect the information you choose to give us. When you submit our quote
        request form, we collect the details you provide — such as your name, company, email
        address, phone number, order volume, and any message you send. We do not sell this
        information or share it with third parties for their own marketing.
      </p>

      <h2>How we use it</h2>
      <p>
        We use the information you submit solely to respond to your inquiry, prepare a quote,
        and communicate with you about our services. Form submissions are delivered to us by
        email through our form provider, Web3Forms.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
      <p>
        Our website does not use advertising cookies or track you across other sites. If we
        add basic, privacy-respecting analytics in the future to understand overall site
        traffic, it will not personally identify you.
      </p>

      <h2>Data retention</h2>
      <p>
        We keep quote requests only as long as needed to serve you and maintain our business
        records. You may ask us to delete your information at any time.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact us</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this policy or your information? Contact us at
        <a href="mailto:trevor@ozarkfulfillment.com">trevor@ozarkfulfillment.com</a> or
        (417) 453-1005.
      </p>

      <p class="back"><a href="/">← Back to home</a></p>
    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

<style>
  .legal {
    padding: 3.5rem 0 4.5rem;
  }

  .legal .container {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .legal h1 {
    color: var(--navy-800);
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.4rem);
    margin-bottom: 0.35rem;
  }

  .updated {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .legal h2 {
    color: var(--navy-800);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .legal p {
    color: var(--ink-soft);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal a {
    color: var(--water);
  }

  .back {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
